p.seg:
With these witnesses: the lord William of Mordington; the lord Alan of Swinton;
                  the lord Adam of Prenderguest; Walter, Andrew, Alexander of
                  Paxton; William, vicar of Oldcambus; Robert son of Gregory;
                  Ada of Little Reston; Bertram his son; John, son of Elias of
                  Over Ayton; Maurice son of Merlin; Ralph, grieve of
                  Coldingham; Roger, his son; Adam son of Eilaf of Auchencrow;
                  David of Quixwood; and many others.
